name: Ben & Holly Royal Picnic Game
description:
Official Licensed Ben & Holly Merchandise 

Ben & Holly’s Little Kingdom Royal Picnic Game is a magical electronic board game where players have to help Ben & Holly perfect Holly’s misplaced magic spells and transform the animals back to their fairy and elf characters.
To start the game, players must choose a Ben & Holly playing piece and then the players who Birthday it is next must roll the dice and move that amount of spaces around the board. If you are land on a space with an animal picture on it you can pick up the corresponding animal card that can be found around the outside of the game board. If you land on a space with a picture of the magic picnic basket on, then you can take Holly’s magic wand and wave it over the top of the picnic basket and listen carefully because; if you hear a ‘Hurray’ then Holly’s magic has worked and you can flip over your animal card to reveal the character on the other side. But if you hear an ‘Ehm what went wrong?’ sound, then Holly’s magic spell hasn’t worked properly and you cannot turn over your animal card. When players land on or pass the starting space, they are allowed another turn and if you roll the dice and have to move your character to the same space as another player, then you are allowed to jump one space ahead. The winner is the first player to transfer all of their collected animal cards.

This magical game is suitable for 2 – 4 children aged 3 and above. Playing this game with friends and family will help develop children’s counting and social skills from a young age.

Contents:
1 x Magic Picnic Basket 
1 x Magic Wand 
4 x Ben & Holly figurines with plastic stands 
20 x Cards 
1 x Dice and the Game rules 

Battery Operated (2 xAAA batteries not included)
